So, I asked Joan for
all my peer reviews,

31:05.974 --> 31:07.451
and she sent them to me.

31:07.794 --> 31:13.136
She said there were some
not-so-nice ones in here.

31:13.208 --> 31:14.996
Let's read them together.

31:15.649 --> 31:17.769
Ready? Zoey...

31:17.794 --> 31:19.572
"Stammers too much".

31:19.597 --> 31:20.972
