31:32.192 --> 31:34.605
"I deserved the promotion, not her."

31:35.785 --> 31:36.808
I wrote that one.

31:36.833 --> 31:38.589
I'm shocked.

31:39.156 --> 31:42.445
Look, reading these
comments hurts, a lot.

31:42.470 --> 31:43.980
Very deeply.

31:44.005 --> 31:46.250
Quite a bit more than I
was expecting them to.

31:46.522 --> 31:48.741
But once we've taken in that criticism,

31:48.766 --> 31:51.171
it's all about how we pick ourselves up

31:51.196 --> 31:52.851
and bounce right back.

31:52.876 --> 31:55.421
