33:12.847 --> 33:15.165
You're shutting down the business?

33:16.033 --> 33:17.618
How can I keep going?

33:17.643 --> 33:21.400
I mean, all this time,
it's always been the two of us.

33:21.425 --> 33:25.298
And what, I'm supposed
to just forge on alone?

33:25.323 --> 33:28.533
