35:49.480 --> 35:53.314
Just so we're clear, I'm doing this.

36:08.681 --> 36:10.353
Really? Are you sure?

36:10.378 --> 36:13.892
Because I don't have to.

36:13.917 --> 36:15.493
So...

36:16.920 --> 36:19.900
buzz now or forever hold your peace.

36:41.582 --> 36:42.980
Okay.

