37:13.278 --> 37:14.353
for love and attention,

37:14.378 --> 37:17.079
so she's making me look
like a horror villain.

37:17.104 --> 37:20.711
<i>I don't mind it. So, I, uh,
decided to take some initiative...</i>

37:20.736 --> 37:22.579
_

37:23.262 --> 37:25.103
<i>... and I broke up with Autumn.</i>

37:26.630 --> 37:31.299
